            &lt;div class=&quot;relative min-w-[120px] w-[120px]&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;img alt=&quot;习近平同李在明通话 吁加强中韩各层级各领域交流增进战略互信&quot; title=&quot;习近平同李在明通话 吁加强中韩各层级各领域交流增进战略互信&quot; src=&quot;https://cassette.sphdigital.com.sg/image/zaobao/d955c66a7ff990d77873271a8bd6d3b0bb99e0e5ba7a0119a38183def4f3d7bc&quot; class=&quot;my-0 w-full rounded-[4px] object-contain&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;
